    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute gem! Honestly, it's in such incredible, mint condition that you'd think it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for a ride that's been loved and kept in top-notch shape, you've found it! I'm happy to chat and answer any questions you have\u2014let's get you behind the wheel of this beauty!",
      "price": 42900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
